text: Fort-Mardyck is a former commune in the Nord department in north France. Since 9 December 2010, it is part of the commune of Dunkirk.La Voix du Nord 8 December 2010INSEE In 2019, 3,403 people lived there.Téléchargement du fichier d'ensemble des populations légales en 2019, INSEE == References == Category:Former communes in Nord Category:Dunkirk
